3567.Description:
Several functions that help for working with item properties. Can be used as an include file (which is what I do).

int ip_to_int(itemproperty ip);

Converts an itemproperty data type to a single integer for portability such as to store in a local variable.

itemproperty int_to_ip(int param);

Converts the integer back into an itemproperty.

string ip_to_string(itemproperty ip);

Creates a string description of the item property as it would appear on the item description.

